  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDataArrayComparator  
    IDataComparator  
    IDataIterator  
    IDataParser
    Generic interface for serializing and deserializing IData documents.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicIDataArrayComparator
    Compares two IData[] objects using by comparing each item's keys and values.
    BasicIDataArrayComparator.Holder
    Initialization on demand holder idiom.
    BasicIDataComparator
    Compares two IData objects using all the keys and values in each document.
    BasicIDataComparator.Holder
    Initialization on demand holder idiom.
    CriteriaBasedIDataComparator
    Compares two IData objects using the values associated with the given list of keys in precedence order.
    IDataComparisonCriterion
    Defines a single criterion used by the IDataComparator class.
    IDataEnvelope
    A convenience wrapper for an IData object, that implements the IData, IDataCodable, IDataPortable, and ValuesCodable interfaces for maximum API compatibility.
    IDataHelper
    A collection of convenience methods for working with IData objects.
    IDataHelper.CompoundKey
    Represents a compound key which can be used for grouping IData documents together.
    IDataKey
    Convenience class for fully qualified IData keys.
    IDataKey.Part
    Represents an individual key part of a fully-qualified key.
    IDataMap
    Wraps an IData document in an implementation of the Iterable, Comparable, and Map interfaces.
    IDataMap.IDataIteratorImplementation
    Implementation class for an IDataIterator.
    IDataTextParser
    Serializes and deserializes IData documents to and from a text representation.
    IDataXMLParser
    Deserializes and serializes IData objects from and to XML.
    IDataXMLParser.Holder
    Initialization on demand holder idiom.
    ReadOnlyIDataMap  
    ReadOnlyIDataMap.ReadOnlyIDataCursor
    Read-only wrapper for an IDataCursor.
    ReadOnlyIDataMap.ReadOnlyIDataSharedCursor
    Read-only wrapper for an IDataSharedCursor.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    IDataComparisonType
    The different types of IData value comparison supported by the IDataComparator class.
